OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FSeven people from across the Channel
OL,7,FIslands had their service recognised
OL,8,Fin King Charles' Birthday Honours list.
OL,10,FAmong them were four people from
OL,11,FGuernsey and three from Jersey.
OL,13,FHis Excellency, Lieutenant General Sir
OL,14,FRichard Cripwell KBE CB, commented: "I
OL,15,Fcontinue to be hugely impressed by the
OL,16,Feffort made by islanders to volunteer
OL,17,Ftheir time and energy to support
OL,18,Fcharitable causes, sport and their
OL,19,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
