PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,F"The commitment of those honoured
OL,7,Ftoday is truly humbling, and they are
OL,8,Fthoroughly deserving of national
OL,9,Frecognition. I congratulate them all."
OL,11,FMembers of the Order of the British
OL,12,FEmpire (MBE)
OL,14,FJason Wyse is the CEO of Silkworth,
OL,15,Fwhich delivers addiction treatment to
OL,16,Findividuals and their families in
OL,17,FJersey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
