OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FFounded in the 1990s, the charity aims
OL,7,Fto be "a force of healing and hope",
OL,8,Fwith alcohol consumption levels being
OL,9,Ftwice as high as those in the UK, and
OL,10,Fone of the highest in Europe.
OL,12,FJason has been leading the charity
OL,13,Fsince 2008, having previously held
OL,14,Fseveral senior roles in the finance
OL,15,Findustry.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/14
