OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FThe charity describes him as "a key
OL,7,Ffigure and expert voice in his field,
OL,8,Fand provides many presentations around
OL,9,FJersey and the UK, to professionals
OL,10,Fand students about addiction and
OL,11,Ftreatment options".
OL,13,FMike Haden receives his honour for
OL,14,Fservices to the community in his role
OL,15,Fat Hands Around the World Jersey.
OL,17,FThe charity supports schools and
OL,18,Fchildren in Rwanda; Mr Haden has been
OL,19,Ftravelling to the area for the last 16
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
