OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FHands Around the World now works with
OL,7,Fnine schools to build new classrooms
OL,8,Fand facilities, as well as providing
OL,9,Fsanitary products to girls.
OL,11,FMike stressed that the award was about
OL,12,Fthe team around him, adding his
OL,13,Fmotivation is "the pride of what local
OL,14,Fpeople are doing for themselves".
OL,16,F"It's fantastic for the charity to
OL,17,Fshow people what we've been doing
OL,18,Fthere," he told ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/14
