OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,F"It's not just the money that us and
OL,7,FJersey Overseas Aid have put in, it's
OL,8,Ftheir own efforts."
OL,10,FJurat Ian Brown
OL,12,FJurat Ian Brown is a keen cyclist,
OL,13,Frepresenting Guernsey at seven Island
OL,14,FGames and two Commonwealth Games. He
OL,15,Fwas also the first cyclist to
OL,16,Frepresent Great Britain in the Tour of
OL,17,FNormandy.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
