CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FSince then, he has run a cycling shop
OL,7,Fin Guernsey and raised large sums of
OL,8,Fmoney for charity, which he finds
OL,9,F"satisfying and rewarding".
OL,11,FHis project, Wheels for You, aims to
OL,12,Fimprove access to cycling for people
OL,13,Fwho cannot ride traditional, two-wheel
OL,14,Fbikes.
OL,16,FAnother one of his projects is the
OL,17,FRock to Rocque charity cycle ride,
OL,18,Fwhich has raised more than #700,000 in
OL,19,Fthe last 34 years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/14
