OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FHe found out about his award two weeks
OL,7,Fago and told ITV News that he is still
OL,8,F"in a state of shock".
OL,10,FBritish Empire Medals (BEM)
OL,12,FJohanna Norman
OL,14,FJo Norman has been awarded a British
OL,15,FEmpire Medal after nearly five decades
OL,16,Fof voluntary services to swimming and
OL,17,Fwater safety in Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
