PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FShe began teaching swimming in the
OL,7,F1970s and has coached athletes
OL,8,Fcompeting at the Island, Commonwealth,
OL,9,Fand Olympic Games.
OL,11,FLater, she established the Open Castle
OL,12,FCharity Swim and raised tens of
OL,13,Fthousands of pounds for local causes.
OL,15,FNominated for the Guernsey Press Pride
OL,16,Fof Guernsey Awards in 2024, Jo was
OL,17,Fdescribed as "essential" to the
OL,18,FGuernsey Swimming Club, winning the
OL,19,FSports Volunteer of the Year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/14
