OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FBen Gregg has been recognised for his
OL,7,Fservices to St Martin's Parish in
OL,8,FGuernsey.
OL,10,FHe has been a member of the Parish
OL,11,FDouzaine for 26 years and devoted
OL,12,Fthousands of hours to local
OL,13,Fcampaigning for improved
OL,14,Finfrastructure.
OL,16,FBen also served as the Dean of the
OL,17,FDouzaine until retiring in 2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
