FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FIn a parish newsletter, Senior
OL,7,FConstable Dave Beausire described Ben
OL,8,Fas "a great servant to the parish with
OL,9,Fhis leadership, building knowledge and
OL,10,Fhands-on approach quite literally,
OL,11,Fwith his involvement in the
OL,12,Frefurbishment".
OL,14,FAlongside his parish commitments, he
OL,15,Fhas been a regular volunteer minibus
OL,16,Fdriver for Age Concern and a dedicated
OL,17,Fsupporter of the Multiple Sclerosis
OL,18,FSociety, to which he has contributed
OL,19,Fgenerously over many years.
OL,21,FDawn Tinley
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/14
