OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FDawn Tinley has been recognised for
OL,7,Fservices to people with learning
OL,8,Fdisabilities in Jersey. She is a
OL,9,Fcommittee member at Mencap Jersey and
OL,10,Fhas worked there for nearly four
OL,11,Fdecades.
OL,13,FThroughout her career, she has sought
OL,14,Fto reduce the stigma that disabled
OL,15,Fpeople feel in their everyday lives.
OL,16,FThat has involved a wide variety of
OL,17,Fprograms, including placing them in
OL,18,Fsupported private accommodation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
