PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781543165
OL,3,CThe seven Channel Islanders recognised
OL,4,Cin the King's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FMrs Tinley found out about her award
OL,7,Fwhen a phone call from the governor
OL,8,Finterrupted her pilates class. She
OL,9,Ftold ITV News that at first, she
OL,10,Fthought it was a "wind-up".
OL,12,FWhen she eventually discovered that it
OL,13,Fwas real, she says she was
OL,14,F"gobsmacked".
OL,16,FRoyal Victorian Order (Silver)
OL,18,FColin Prigent
OL,20,FColin is the Deputy Head Gardener at
OL,21,FGovernment House.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/14
